  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/3608d95bacdaa99e2a4f35de4bf71b7a.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=72 /></span>You stand outside a house on the edge of town, dragged there by a couple of guys you can't say no to without getting your kneecaps busted, and told that you were helping them to rob it. It's only three sisters who live there, they said. It's an easy score, they said. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You sneak inside and start searching the rooms, as instructed. It's dark, and even though you don't see anything worth taking, things are going smoothly so far. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then the screaming starts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/08809b1a902ccd10f61393a8d383f571.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=72 /></span>Hide from what's hunting you. Use anything in the house to further your escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every action you take will affect how your story evolves. Do your best to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/74e9d06a67f0abf0f209b68887fa7a33.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/17bea45b572ee190839bcfc263275659.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/718a32223926a5e9bbdfec1fae8cf690.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/3f56eed97de655786440aabfc291559c.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>An Escape-Room Horror Game</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sneak, hide, and use the environment to survive long enough to escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hand-Drawn Art</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With beautiful hand-drawn art of the unique characters from a number of guest artists! Do you recognize them all?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/3608d95bacdaa99e2a4f35de4bf71b7a.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=72 /></span>You stand outside a house on the edge of town, dragged there by a couple of guys you can't say no to without getting your kneecaps busted, and told that you were helping them to rob it. It's only three sisters who live there, they said. It's an easy score, they said. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You sneak inside and start searching the rooms, as instructed. It's dark, and even though you don't see anything worth taking, things are going smoothly so far. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then the screaming starts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/08809b1a902ccd10f61393a8d383f571.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=72 /></span>Hide from what's hunting you. Use anything in the house to further your escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every action you take will affect how your story evolves. Do your best to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/74e9d06a67f0abf0f209b68887fa7a33.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/17bea45b572ee190839bcfc263275659.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/718a32223926a5e9bbdfec1fae8cf690.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2300920/extras/3f56eed97de655786440aabfc291559c.avif?t=1749385644\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>An Escape-Room Horror Game</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sneak, hide, and use the environment to survive long enough to escape. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hand-Drawn Art</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With beautiful hand-drawn art of the unique characters from a number of guest artists! Do you recognize them all?</p>",
